text: janarallobbanu, navu allahanannu nambidevu ennuttane. Adare a balika allahana margadalli tannannu satayisaladare, janarinda banda parikseyannu avanu allahana sikse embante pariganisuttane. Innu nim'ma odeyana sahaya bandare khanditavagiyu avaru, navu nim'ma jotege iddevu ennuttare. Lokadelledeya janara manas'sugalalli enide embudu allahanige cennagi tiliyade
